<div class='layout'><p>Chapter 68</p><p>68</p></div>
<div class='layout'><p>The appliance store dealers mustache……clearly as lush as it……been in……younger days,……it……grizzled now, even though……hair on……head……still black. He touched……mustache……of sheer habit as he gazed at Dors……brushed it back on each side.</p><p>用品店老板的八字胡显然和年轻时代一样浓密，只是如今已经斑白，虽说他的头发乌黑依旧。他一面凝视着铎丝，一面伸手将那两撇胡子往后梳，全然是一种习惯性动作。</p></div>
